Keyword::Declare version 0.000005

Declare new Perl keywords with a keyword: 'keyword'

See the examples in the demo/ and dlib/ subdirectories.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

Keyword::Simple
PPI


